# Phase 1 audit reports — output directory
#
# This folder is produced by `scripts/review/run-audit.sh`.
# Most outputs are reproducible from source and not committed; only the
# narrative reports (AUDIT.md, BACKLOG.md, WONTFIX.md, FINAL.md, etc.)
# are checked in to PR-2 / PR-5.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!AUDIT.md
!AUDIT-SUMMARY.md
!BACKLOG.md
!WONTFIX.md
!FINAL.md
!nav-exclude-decisions.md
!pilot-results.md
!level-*-changes.md
!baseline-build.log
!inventory.csv
